fields.name: Westfield Tea Tree Plaza
fields.description: Westfield Tea Tree Plaza is a large shopping centre located in Modbury serving as a shopping hub for Adelaide's growing north eastern suburbs.

fields.name: Westfield Marion
fields.description: Westfield Marion is the largest shopping complex in Adelaide, South Australia, located in Oaklands Park, serving greater Southern Adelaide.

fields.name: University of South Australia
fields.description: The University of South Australia is a public research university in the Australian state of South Australia. It is the largest university in South Australia with more than 32,000 students.

fields.name: University of Adelaide
fields.description: The University of Adelaide is a public university located in Adelaide, South Australia. Established in 1874, it is the third-oldest university in Australia.

fields.name: Mayfair Hotel
fields.description: Chic rooms and suites with 55-inch flat-screens in an upmarket hotel with dining & 5 meeting spaces.

fields.name: Peppers Waymouth Hotel
fields.description: Modern choice offering chic rooms, plus a relaxed restaurant, a hip lounge and an indoor pool.

fields.name: Adelaide Zoo
fields.description: Adelaide Zoo is Australia's second oldest zoo, and like other leading zoos in Australia, including Melbourne Zoo, Taronga Zoo, and Perth Zoo it is operated on a non-profit basis.

fields.name: South Australian Meseum
fields.description: The South Australian Museum is a natural history museum and research institution in Adelaide, South Australia, founded in 1856. It occupies a complex of buildings on North Terrace in the cultural precinct of the Adelaide Parklands.

fields.name: South Australian Maritime Meseum
fields.description: The South Australian Maritime Museum is a state government museum, part of the History Trust of South Australia.

fields.name: Orana
fields.description: Upscale Modern Australian tasting menu in an elegant, intimate restaurant with timber styling.

fields.name: Appellation Restaurant
fields.address: Seppeltsfield Rd & Stonewell Rd, Marananga SA 5355
fields.description: Elegant Modern Australian cuisine and choice Barossa wines in a bright, sophisticated setting.

fields.name: Monarto Zoo
fields.address: Old Princes Hwy, Monarto South SA 5254
fields.description: Monarto Zoological Park is a 1,500-hectare open range zoo located in South Australia administered by the Royal Zoological Society of South Australia. It is located at Monarto approximately 70 kilometres from Adelaide's centre.

fields.name: State Library of South Australia
fields.address: North Terrace & Kintore Ave, Adelaide SA 5000
fields.description: The State Library of South Australia, located on North Terrace, Adelaide, is the official library of the Australian state of South Australia.

fields.name: Deep Creak Conservation Park
fields.address: Boat Harbor Rd, Deep Creek SA 5204
fields.description: Deep Creek Conservation Park is a protected area in the Australian state of South Australia located on the southern coast of Fleurieu Peninsula in the gazetted localities of Deep Creek and Delamere about 11 kilometres east of Cape Jervis.
